ooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DpyMtW05C0h8C%26pg%3DPA15%26dq%3Driver%2Bcivilization%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DX%26ei%3DUbcyVNSFF4rWiwLkzIGICQ%26ved%3D0CCcQ6AEwAjgK%23v%3Donepage%26q%3Driver%2520civilization%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARiver+valley+civilization\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rivervalleycivilizations.com/indus.html\">\"Indus River Valley Civilization\"</a>. <i>The River Valley Civilization Guide</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">27 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+River+Valley+Civilization+Guide&amp;rft.atitle=Indus+River+Valley+Civilization&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rivervalleycivilizations.com%2Findus.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARiver+valley+civilization\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Adrian Cole and Stephen Ortega, The Thinking Past (New York: Oxford University Press, 2015), 83, 95-101.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Adrian Cole and Stephen Ortega, The Thinking Past (New York: Oxford University Press, 2015), 83, 95-101.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Adrian Cole and Stephen Ortega, The Thinking Past (New York: Oxford University Press, 2015), 106-108.</span>\n</li